        "zh": "(1) 廣告概論<br>(2) 廣告類型<br>(3) 廣告創意 <br>(4) 廣告策略<br>(5) 廣告表現方式 <br>(6) 平面廣告設計<br>(7) 活動企劃<br>(8) 活動執行與檢討<br>",
        "en": "(1) Introduction to advertising<br>(2) Type of advertisement<br>(3) Advertising ideas<br>(4) Advertising strategy<br>(5) Advertising performance<br>(6) Graphic design<br>(7) Activity planning<br>(8) Activity execution and review<br>"
